- `kernel/src/arch/aarch64/mmu.rs` — add `assert_tcr_el1_as_8bit()`,
  `switch_ttbr0_with_asid(asid_tagged_ttbr0)`, and
  `enable_ttbr0_walks_once()`. Remove (or repurpose) `activate_user_ttbr0`'s
  single-shot model.
