  code/stack frame allocation + `map_page`. Store `ttbr0_pa` and `asid` into
  the proc slot. Call `mmu::enable_ttbr0_walks_once()` once at the top.
- `kernel/src/proc/sched.rs` — `schedule_next` swaps TTBR0 (ASID-tagged) +
