//! stub blob is copied in via HHDM (`mm::phys_to_hhdm`), and the
//! resulting `(ttbr0_pa, asid)` is stored on the proc slot. The scheduler
//! ([`crate::proc::sched::schedule_next`]) installs that TTBR0 on every
//! EL1 → EL0 transition.
